'''Nkangala''' ke Masepala Setereke gofeta diporofense [[Mpumalanga]] kamoka [[Afrika Borwa]]. 

Seat ya Nkangala ke [[Middelburg, Mpumalanga|Middelburg]]. Setšhaba se 1,308,129, e 319,920 ba bulela [[Sendebele]] (2011 Palo ya batho). District code ke DC30.

